divs: Sighting DetailsWent outside to drive to work, looked up at the sky and saw a large, bright, white light that did not blink moving quickly and silently through the sky. Lost sight of the object when it moved behind a tree and disappeared. We are not sure what it was. To big and bright to be a satellite like we see through our telescope. Very visible with the naked eye, it seemed to gradually move faster and faster
Summary: Bright,white light. Did not blink. Fast moving from northwest to southeast.
trends: There have been no other sightings in Curlew
This sighting has never been favorited.
